HEADWORD: detribalization
<hw>detribalization</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the act of causing tribal
people to abandon their customs and adopt urban ways of
living.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> detribalisation.</syn>⟦br⟧
